    <item>
      <title>Additional information for applicant&#39;s review</title>
      <link>https://apophenian.art/249-a-street-coop-application/additional-info/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://apophenian.art/249-a-street-coop-application/additional-info/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Have you previously had a working studio? Please include locations and&#xA;dates.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I have not had a previous working studio. I did apply for a studio residency at&#xA;BCA last year, but was unsuccessful.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. What is your art training (art school, private, self taught)?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I studied art education during my undergrad teaching degree. See my résumé for&#xA;more details about my experience.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Please enter a brief artist&amp;rsquo;s statement or information about your&#xA;work/studio practice.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
